2018-05-30T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美方搞錯了一點，那就是貿易戰不是一般的戰爭。後者可以打到對方的國土上，如果順利的話，甚至可以有「零傷亡」的奇跡。但是貿易戰一定是相互損失的，一方對一方壓倒性勝利的貿易戰決不會有，更何況<span style=\"color: red;\">當美國面對中國這個市場規模與它差不多的對手時</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哇好撚屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n那兒來的自信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ce589d067f4946ac949d57ea5d033a61feaa9d","tid":683654,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:33:35.000Z","msg":"韓國/台灣 : 「不能不說，今天的世界面臨一個極不確定的中國政府... 達成一個協議，然後就提高要價，力圖再要一個對自己更有利的協議，這不是文明世界的規則，我國也決不會做慣中國這個壞習慣的配合者。」<br />\n同一篇文真係好適合做東亞各國寫翻畀中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開始先大量同你各類產品大量入口<br />\n之後時機成熟再搵名目反韓/台獨就停止進口<br />\n搞死當地各行各業，今日畀人玩撚翻轉頭<br />\n你話係咪求仁得仁? <br />\n中國又成為最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1dd661f6350a5d90e56c6806e4b8ab2be4c0b7c","tid":683654,"uid":156005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:35:43.000Z","msg":"環球時報：咪逼我中國亮劍！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b71dc1fd816a689151926cbfa66883c3160227","tid":683654,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dc86d003ebe7269df990f27089eac5587b258f5","tid":683654,"uid":38523,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T01:24:38.000Z","msg":"這不是文明世界的規則，中國也決不會做慣美國這個壞習慣的配合者<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited